				\begin{document}$$t_{jl} = {\text{var}} \left( {\ln \frac{{x_{j} }}{{y_{l} }}} \right),j,\,l = 1, \ldots ,D$$\end{document}tjl=varlnxjyl,j,l=1,…,D
